        {
          content: '<h1 style="margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: left; line-height: 37px;"><span style="background: white; font-size: 24px;">使用沙箱环境</span></h1><h2 style="margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: left; line-height: 37px;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size:24px;font-family:宋体">沙箱环境</span></strong></h2><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: left; "><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">沙箱环境是协助开发者进行接口功能开发及主要功能联调的辅助环境。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">沙箱环境模拟了开放银行平台主要功能和运行逻辑，支持列表中的API接</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">口均已开通权限，可以在线联调测试</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">。 </span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">开发者应用上线审核</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">之</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">前，可以</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">结合自身场景</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">需求，</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">确定API之后先</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">在沙箱环境中了解、组合和调试</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">相关API</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">接口，从而帮助开发者在应用上线审核完成</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">之后</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">能够</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">更快速、更顺利的进行线上</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">运行</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">和验收工作。</span></p><h2><strong style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size:24px;font-family:宋体">使用步骤</span></strong></h2><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size:24px;font-family:宋体"></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">为了方便</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">开发者调试应用接口</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">，沙箱环境</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">采用</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">独立</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">于生产</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">环境的配置，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">平台自动为每个开发者创建一个沙箱应用，</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">提供了辅助开发者测试开放</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">API</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">接口的</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">数据和</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">工具。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">开发者登录后进入应用中心，点击沙箱应用入口，</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">查看沙箱应用</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">详情页</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">信息</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体">，</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">配置沙箱环境的密钥即可开始开发</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">调试</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">。</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">图</span></strong><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体"><br/></span></p><p></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">配置完成之后，开发者按照接入步骤或集成SDK，在自己的应用工程代码中配置相关信息，应用运行发起API至开放银行平台沙箱环境联调测试。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">1.沙箱APPID；</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">2.沙箱网关；</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">3.沙箱SM2应用私钥(用于签名)；</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">4.沙箱SM2平台公钥(用于验签)；</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体">5.沙箱SM4应用密钥(用于加密)；</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:宋体"><br/></span></strong><br/></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size:24px;font-family:宋体"><br/></span></strong><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size:24px;font-family:宋体"><br/></span></strong><br/></p><p><span style="background: white; font-size: 24px;"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>',
